MCG 






Select Page


  
 



 



 










 





 

Merion Capital Group 

A company is only as extraordinary as its people.
Are you ready to join an extraordinary team?  

Join Our Team 

Read Our  Research 


 



 
 






Fully Independent
Merion is privately owned by the founders of the Firm.  Our vision was to create a robust independent platform built for the new economy.

 
 
 




Scope
Merion is registered in all 50 states and two US Territories. Through our affiliates, we also offer global solutions and have clients on four continents.

 
 
 




Capabilities
We are approved to conduct eleven lines of business for institutions and individuals and have access to over 50,000 financial products including alternatives.

 
 
 
 





Compliance
Our Firm is dedicated to staying ahead of the rapidly changing regulatory landscape and highly experienced in all aspects of B/D compliance.

 
 
 




Technology
We fully integrate 21st century technology to manage our business. This allows us to be more efficient and provide the security and peace of mind that our clients require.

 
 
 




Platform Agnostic
We have long term relationships with many custodians, broker/dealers, RIAs, fund families, and family offices to be able to match the client need with the ideal solution.

 
 
 
 
 





Reports Published

 


Buy-side Clients

 


Registered Representatives

 
 
 



Capital Markets
 
MCG specializes in providing investment banking and broker dealer services to companies of all sizes ranging from development stage to mid-capitalization public companies. We work with companies in a variety of industries including the financial services sector, which is an area of specialization. The Firm’s professionals have been involved in capital markets transactions for over three decades on both the buy-side and sell-side of the deals. We provide a full range of investment banking services, including strategic and capital market transactions, equity trading and sales, equity research, and other consulting services. By developing strategic partnerships with our clients, and aligning our interest with those of the company, our professionals believe we can better help our clients creatively deal with the dynamics of the business and regulatory environment.
 
 
 





Investment Banking
We provide a host of strategic and capital markets transactions and advisory services, including: Corporate Valuations, Fairness Opinions, Mergers, Acquisitions and Divestitures, Strategic Transaction Planning, Due Diligence Services, and Financings-Recapitalizations

 
 
 




Capital Raises
Our team has participated in a wide variety of capital raises that have ranged in size from $5 million to more than $100 million. We have the ability to lead certain deals while in others we have played a supporting role by finding both institutional and high-net worth investors.

 
 
 




Mergers & Acquisitions
MCG assists clients in many aspects of M&A and divestitures. Our start to finish participation includes Strategy Development, Target Identification, Market Research, Competitive Analysis, Due Diligence, Transaction Structuring, Negotiation, Regulatory and Compliance Assistance and Fairness Opinions.

 
 
 
 
 




Research, Sales & Trading
 
Equity research and sales is a core competency of the Firm. We provide global macroeconomic commentary and in-depth research on companies in the financial services sector that caters specifically to institutional asset managers. The objective is simple: to generate as much value as possible for our clients through differentiated thoughts and opinions, research, investment ideas, and management access opportunities. Our clientele includes many of the largest asset managers in the U.S., as well as premier hedge funds and other general and boutique institutional investors. Our research publications include: Daily Market Updates, Global Macro Notes, Initial Reports, Company Updates, Earnings Previews, Earnings Reviews, Monthly Statistical Reviews, Trading Signal Alerts, and other notes and commentaries.
 
 


