Product Distribution
 
Merion Capital Group’s product distribution team represents a leading issuer of new issue structured notes and market-linked CD’s to financial advisors at national and regional broker-dealers, banks and independent firm levels. These offerings are geared for advisors who aim to provide “correction protection” for their clients’ portfolios. Structured Investments provide an alternative, or complement, to traditional long-only investments. These product solutions can offer unique risk-return profiles to address investment objectives, such as risk management, periodic income, and the potential for enhanced returns. Structured investments can address advisor concerns such as risk, yield generation, access to new markets and portfolio diversification.
 
 
 





Market Leader
Our team has participated in a wide variety of capital raising efforts that ranged in size from $5 million to more than $100 million.

 
 
 




Expanding Opportunity
Retail structured products are a growing niche in the investing marketplace that offer several unique features and characteristics compared to traditional products.

 
 
 




Large Universe
Our distribution channels include over 30,000 financial advisors located in every state in the US.

 
 
 
 
 




Private Client Group
 
Our Firm provides a robust platform coupled with supportive environment that allows financial advisors to provide all the investment and service needs for their clients. We have access to a host of leading technology solutions, traditional and proprietary investment products, including alternative strategies, as well as the registrations and approvals to bring almost any appropriate and suitable solution to our clients. In addition, we provide our advisors and clients access to a wealth of information and insight on the latest economic news, market events, and trends.
 
 
 





Fully Independent
Merion is privately owned by the founders of the Firm.  Our vision was to create a robust independent platform built for the new economy.

 
 
 




Transition
We have a dedicated and experienced team to facilitate the onboarding of new clients, advisors and product solutions.

 
 
 


