Merion Capital Group is a Broker Dealer specializing in a variety of businesses, which include capital markets, product distribution, research, private placements, and other institutional and individual client lines. The Firm is registered with the Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (“FINRA”) and a member of the Securities Investor Protection Corporation (“SIPC”).
